<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Vision</title>

  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      background-color: #FF9F00;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    main {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding-top: 80px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .vision-sheet {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 900px;
      padding: 60px;
      background-color: #FFFFFF;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .vision-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .pattern {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }

    .image {
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .image img {
      width: 300px;
      height: 200px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .vision-container {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .image img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
      }

      .pattern {
        text-align: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navbar stays on top -->
  <%- include("navbar") %>

  <!-- Main content comes below -->
  <main>
    <div class="vision-sheet">
      <h1>Your Vision</h1>

      <div class="vision-container">
        <div class="pattern">
          At MYNGO, our vision is to build a world where every individual has the opportunity,
          resources, and support to live a life of dignity, purpose, and fulfillment. We strive to create
          lasting impact through community-driven initiatives, empowering people to rise above challenges
          and contribute to a more just, equitable, and compassionate society.
        </div>

        <div class="image">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dosmitdnl/image/upload/v1754122773/AdiYuvan/xfvyxg38menwe1w8zeew.jpg" alt="Vision Image" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
